text: Up Front Tour was a concert tour by American singer Diana Ross in 1983 associated with Ross 1983 album. On this tour Diana played in Central Park during the legendary concert under the rain. ==References== * https://web.archive.org/web/20150710201051/http://www.dianaross.de/ * http://www.dianarossofficialfanclub.wordpress.com/concerts-tours/ Category:1983 concert tours Category:Diana Ross concert tours
title: Up Front Tour
